  "title" : "Implementing a one to many map in Java",
  "body" : "<p>Have one <code>object</code> of <code>type A</code> that is related to a bunch of <code>objects</code> of <code>type B</code> and want to store all <code>objects</code> of <code>type A</code> and easily access their <code>type B</code> relations.</p>\n\n<p>What's the best (built-in?) data structure doing this in Java?</p>\n"
